ed="T" n="0864b17"/><persName key="A013551">釋元皎</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000047120">靈武</placeName>人也。有志操，與眾不群，以<lb
ed="T" n="0864b18"/>持明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g249"/>為<anchor xml:id="beg0864sgsz10"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0864sgsz10"/>務。<date key="j19960861997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15" notBefore-iso="+0752-12-30"><name>天寶</name>末</date>，<persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>幸<placeName key="PL000000034805">蜀</placeName>，<persName key="A004378">肅皇</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000047120">靈<lb
ed="T" n="0864b19"/>武</placeName>訓兵，計剋復<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京師</ref><ptr target="#n382"/>。為物議攸同，請<ref type="person" target="#A004378">帝</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0864b20"/>即位，改元<date key="j19974111997993" notAfter-iso="+0758-03-21" notBefore-iso="+0756-08-16"><name>至德</name></date>。及<date key="j19975771997960" notAfter-iso="+0758-02-16" notBefore-iso="+0757-01-29">二年</date>，返轅指<placeName key="PL000000042848">扶風</placeName>，<ref type="person" target="#A004378">帝</ref>素<lb
ed="T" n="0864b21"/>憑<name>釋</name>氏，擇清尚僧首途，若<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1994"/>祓除<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1993"/>然。北土西<lb
ed="T" n="0864b22"/>河所推，<persName key="A013551">皎</persName>應其選，召入受勅旨，隨<ref type="person" target="#A004378">駕</ref>仗內<lb
ed="T" n="0864b23"/>赴<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>。尋勅令<persName key="A013551">皎</persName>向前發，至于<placeName key="PL000000042848">鳳翔</placeName>，於<placeName key="PL000000042790">開元<lb
ed="T" n="0864b24"/>寺</placeName>置御<placeName key="PL000000042791">藥師道場</placeName>。更擇三七僧，六時行道，<lb
ed="T" n="0864b25"/>然燈歌唄，讚念持經，無敢言疲，精潔<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1995"/>可量<lb
ed="T" n="0864b26"/>也。忽於法會內生一叢李樹，有四十九莖，<lb
ed="T" n="0864b27"/>具事奏聞，宣內使驗實。<ref type="person" target="#A004378">帝</ref>大驚喜曰：「此大<lb
ed="T" n="0864b28"/>瑞應。」<date key="j19976821997682" when-iso="+0757-05-14">四月十八日</date>，檢校御<placeName key="PL000000042791">藥師道場</placeName>念誦僧<lb
ed="T" n="0864b29"/><persName key="A013551">元皎</persName>等表賀，答勅曰：「瑞李繁滋，國之興兆。生<pb ed="T" n="0864c" xml:id="T50.2061.0864c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0864c01"/>在伽藍之內，足知覺樹之榮。感此殊祥，與<lb
ed="T" n="0864c02"/><ref type="person" target="#A013551">師</ref>同慶。」<persName key="A013551">皎</persName>之持誦，功能通感，率多此類。加<lb
ed="T" n="0864c03"/>署內供奉焉<ptr target="#n3012"/>。</p>
